SELECT DISTINCT
	"P".SURVEY_TARGET_ID 					AS "SURVEY_KEY",
	"ST"."DATE" AS "VISIT_DATE",
	COALESCE("PRD".SURVEY_KEY,'NOT INFORMED') AS "VISIT_PRODUCT",
	SUM("P".RESPONSE_NUMBER) AS "TOTAL_VISITS"
    
 FROM LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_SURVEY_RESPONSES AS "P"
 
 LEFT JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT
	"P".SURVEY_TARGET_ID 					AS "SURVEY_KEY",
    "P".RESPONSE
 FROM LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_SURVEY_RESPONSES AS "P"
 WHERE "P".QUESTION_ORDER = 0  AND "P".RESPONSE IS NOT NULL) AS "PRD" ON "P".SURVEY_TARGET_ID = "PRD".SURVEY_KEY
 
 INNER JOIN (SELECT 
	  "ST".SURVEY_TARGET_ID as "SURVEY_KEY",
	  CAST(TRIM(CAST(LEFT(CAST("ST".REVIEW_DATE_ID AS CHAR(8)),4)||'-'||
	  SUBSTRING(CAST("ST".REVIEW_DATE_ID AS CHAR(8)) FROM 5 FOR 2) ||'-'||
	  RIGHT(CAST("ST".REVIEW_DATE_ID AS CHAR(8)),2) AS VARCHAR(10))) AS DATE FORMAT 'yyyy-mm-dd') AS "DATE",
	  "ST".SOURCE_LAST_MODIFIED_TS as "TARGET_LAST_MODIFIED_TS",
	  CAST("ST".SOURCE_LAST_MODIFIED_TS AS DATE FORMAT 'YYYYMMDD') AS "MODIFIED_DATE",
	  "ST".START_DATE_ID,
	  "ST".END_DATE_ID,
	  "ST".REVIEW_DATE_ID,
	  "ST".REVIEW_STATUS,
	  "ST".MANAGER_TERRITORY_ID,
	  "ST".EMPLOYEE_TERRITORY_ID,
	  "ST".TERRITORY_ID
FROM LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_SURVEY_TARGETS AS "ST"
WHERE "ST".COUNTRY_CODE = 'BR'  AND 
	"ST".SURVEY_TARGET_NAME LIKE '%GSO U%' AND
	LEFT(CAST("ST".REVIEW_DATE_ID AS CHAR(8)),6) > '201901') AS "ST" ON "P".SURVEY_TARGET_ID = "ST".SURVEY_KEY

WHERE "P".QUESTION_ID = '12215'
GROUP BY "P".SURVEY_TARGET_ID,
			"ST"."DATE",
		COALESCE("PRD".SURVEY_KEY,'NOT INFORMED');

SELECT 
	  QUESTION_ID,
      CREATED_DATE AS "QUESTION_CREATED_DATE",
      QUESTION_NAME,     
      SOURCE_LAST_MODIFIED_TS	AS "QUESTION_LAST_MODIFIED_TS",
      QUESTION_TEXT,
      QUESTION_ORDER 		AS "QUESTION_ORDER",
      CASE
      WHEN QUESTION_ORDER = 0 THEN 'PRODUCT'
      WHEN QUESTION_ORDER = 1 THEN 'COCO'
      WHEN QUESTION_ORDER = 2 THEN 'SOB'
      WHEN QUESTION_ORDER = 3 THEN 'QTC'
      WHEN QUESTION_ORDER = 4 THEN 'GSO'
      WHEN QUESTION_ORDER = 5 THEN 'VISITS'
      ELSE	'' END 	AS "QUESTION_TYPE",
      CASE
      WHEN QUESTION_ORDER = 0 THEN 'PRODUCT' 
      WHEN QUESTION_ORDER = 1 THEN 'OCV'
      WHEN QUESTION_ORDER = 2 THEN 'Foco da Discuss√£o'
      WHEN QUESTION_ORDER = 3 THEN 'Fechamento'
      WHEN QUESTION_ORDER = 4 THEN 'GSO'
      WHEN QUESTION_ORDER = 5 THEN 'Visitas'
      ELSE '' END	AS "TIPO_QUESTAO"
FROM LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_SURVEY_QUESTION
WHERE COUNTRY_CODE = 'BR' AND
QUESTION_ORDER < 6 AND 
DELETED_IND = 0

SELECT RX_EXTERNAL_ID,
      USER_ID,
 	  SOURCE_USER_AID										AS "SF_SOURCE_USER_AID",
      USER_NAME,
      FIRST_NAME,
      NAME,
      LAST_NAME,      
      COUNTRY,
      STATE_PROVINCE,
      UPPER(CITY) 											AS "CITY",
      POSTAL_CODE,
      ACTIVE_IND,
      EMAIL,
      EMPLOYEE_NUMBER_AID,
      USER_IDENTIFIER_AID,
      CORE_GSK_FUNCTIONAL_PROFILE,
      PROFILE_NAME
 FROM  LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_USER
WHERE ACTIVE_IND = 1;
 ;

select DISTINCT MUDID	AS 'RX_EXTERNAL_ID',
 	  UF
from Dim_Cad_Funcionarios

SELECT 
     ROW_ID_FUNCIONARIO										AS RX_EXTERNAL_ID,
	 CICLO,
     CICLO + '-' + ROW_ID_TERRITORIO						AS SALES_FORCE_KEY,
     CICLO + '-' + ROW_ID_TERRITORIO						AS SF_KEY,
	 ROW_ID_TERRITORIO,
     ROW_ID_GD,
     NOME_GD,
     NOME_GR,
	 CASE
     WHEN Len(COALESCE(TERRITORIO_GD,'0123456789')) = 0 THEN TERRITORIO_GD
     ELSE Right(TERRITORIO_GD, 6) END AS TERRITORIO_GD,
	 CASE
	 WHEN Len(COALESCE(TERRITORIO_GR,'0123456789')) = 0 THEN TERRITORIO_GR
     ELSE Right(TERRITORIO_GR, 6)END AS TERRITORIO_GR,
     BU,
     CASE
	 WHEN DIVIS√ÉO = 'REDES' THEN 'REDES DIRETAS'
     ELSE DIVIS√ÉO END  AS DIVIS√ÉO,
     CASE
	 WHEN Len(COALESCE(TERRITORIO,'0123456789')) = 0 THEN TERRITORIO
     ELSE Right(TERRITORIO, 6) END AS TERRITORIO,
	 NOME_REPRESENTANTE										AS NOME_REP        
FROM Dim_Cad_Forca_Vendas
WHERE STATUS = 'A'
  AND CICLO >= '201901'
  AND (BU = 'FARMA' OR BU = 'BIOTECH');

SELECT 
    "CM".CALL_SUMMARY_ID,
     "CM".PARENT_CALL_AID,
     "CM".LOCAL_CALL_DATE_ID,
     "CM".CALL_DATE_ID,
     "CM".TERRITORY_ID,
     LEFT(CAST("CM".CALL_DATE_ID as CHAR(8)),6)         AS "CYCLE",
     ((LEFT(CAST("CM".CALL_DATE_ID as CHAR(8)),6)||'-')||TRIM("CM".TERRITORY_ID))    AS "SALES_FORCE_KEY",
     LEFT(CAST("CM".CALL_DATE_ID as CHAR(8)),6)    AS "DATE",
     "CM".LOCAL_CALL_TIME_ID,
     "CM".ACCOUNT_ID,
     "CM".CALL_NAME,
     "CM".RX_CALL_TYPE,
     "CM".CALL_STATUS,
     "CM".ATTENDEE_TYPE,
     "CM".CLM_IND,
     "CM".SAMPLE_CALL_IND,
     "CM".CALL_TYPE,
     "CM".DETAILED_PRODUCTS,
     "CM".DURATION,
     "CM".CREATED_DATE_ID,
     "CM".CREATED_DATE_TIME_ID,
     "CM".LAST_MODIFIED_DATE_ID,
     "CM".LAST_MODIFIED_DATE_TIME_ID,
     "CM".PRE_CALL_NOTES,
     "CM".NEXT_CALL_NOTES,
     'Completed_vod'                                        AS "REVIEW_STATUS",
     "AC".ACCOUNT_NAME,
     "AC".RX_LEGAL_ID,
     "KEY".KEY_MESSAGE_NAME,
     "KEY".QUESTION_ID,
     COALESCE("KEY".PRODUCT_NAME,'NOT INFORMED') AS "PRODUCT",
     "KEY".CALL_DATE,
     'CALLS'                AS "ORIGEM"

 

FROM  
    LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_CALL_SUMMARY "CM"

 

LEFT JOIN (
            SELECT 
                ACCOUNT_ID,
                 NAME AS "ACCOUNT_NAME",
                 RX_LEGAL_ID
            FROM 
                LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_ACCOUNT
            WHERE
                COUNTRY_CODE = 'BR'
                  AND DELETED_IND = 0
              ) as "AC" ON "CM".ACCOUNT_ID = "AC".ACCOUNT_ID

 

LEFT JOIN (
            SELECT
                "CM".CALL_SUMMARY_ID,
                "KM".KEY_MESSAGE_NAME,
                CASE
                WHEN "KM".KEY_MESSAGE_NAME = 'Tentativa de GSO - Expositiva' THEN '12209'
                WHEN "KM".KEY_MESSAGE_NAME = 'Tentativa de GSO - Interativa' THEN '12213'
                WHEN "KM".KEY_MESSAGE_NAME = 'Lembran√ßa da marca' THEN '12210'
                WHEN "KM".KEY_MESSAGE_NAME = 'Good Sell Outcome (GSO)' THEN '12212'
                ELSE "KM".KEY_MESSAGE_NAME END AS "QUESTION_ID",
                "PC".PRODUCT_NAME,
                "CM".CALL_DATE_ID as "CALL_DATE",
                "CM".TERRITORY_ID  
            
            FROM 
                LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_CALL_MESSAGE as "CM"

 

            LEFT JOIN (
                        SELECT DISTINCT
                            KEY_MESSAGE_ID     as "MESSAGE_ID",
                            KEY_MESSAGE_ID,
                            KEY_MESSAGE_NAME
                        
                        FROM 
                            LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_KEY_MESSAGE
                        WHERE     
                            (KEY_MESSAGE_NAME = 'Visita n√£o promocional' OR
                             KEY_MESSAGE_NAME = 'Lembran√ßa da marca' OR
                             KEY_MESSAGE_NAME LIKE '%GSO%')
                         ) AS "KM" ON "CM".KEY_MESSAGE_ID = "KM".KEY_MESSAGE_ID
        
            LEFT JOIN (
                        SELECT 
                            PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID,
                             PRODUCT_NAME
                        FROM 
                        LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_PRODUCT_CATALOG
                      ) AS "PC" ON "CM".PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID = "PC".PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID
                        
            
                        WHERE 
                        (EXISTS (
                                    SELECT DISTINCT
                                        KEY_MESSAGE_ID     as "MESSAGE_ID",
                                        KEY_MESSAGE_ID,
                                        KEY_MESSAGE_NAME
                                    FROM 
                                        LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_KEY_MESSAGE
                                    WHERE     
                                        (KEY_MESSAGE_NAME = 'Visita n√£o promocional' OR
                                         KEY_MESSAGE_NAME = 'Lembran√ßa da marca' OR
                                         KEY_MESSAGE_NAME LIKE '%GSO%')
                                         AND KEY_MESSAGE_ID = "CM".KEY_MESSAGE_ID)
                                ) 
                        AND
                        (EXISTS (
                                    SELECT 
                                        PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID,
                                         PRODUCT_NAME
                                    FROM 
                                        LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_PRODUCT_CATALOG
                                      WHERE PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID =    "CM".PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID)
                                 )
                         AND
                         LEFT(CAST(CALL_DATE_ID as CHAR(8)),6) > '201901'
        ) AS "KEY" ON "CM".CALL_SUMMARY_ID = "KEY".CALL_SUMMARY_ID
  
WHERE 
    LEFT(CAST("CM".CALL_DATE_ID as CHAR(8)),6)>= '201901' AND
    "CM".COUNTRY_CODE = 'BR' AND 
      "CM".CALL_STATUS = 'Submitted_vod' AND 
      "CM".DELETED_IND = 0
 ORDER BY "SALES_FORCE_KEY";

SELECT 
	"P".SURVEY_TARGET_ID 					AS "SURVEY_KEY",
    "P".QUESTION_ID,					
    "P".SOURCE_CREATED_TS,
    "P".SOURCE_LAST_MODIFIED_TS			AS "RESPONSE_LAST_MODIFIED_TS",
    "P".SOURCE_CREATED_BY_AID AS "SOURCE_USER_AID",
    "P".QUESTION_RESPONSE_ID,          
    "P".RESPONSE_NAME,
    "P".RESPONSE_NUMBER,
    "P".RESPONSE,
    TRIM(COALESCE("PRD".RESPONSE,'NOT INFORMED')) AS "PRODUCT",
    "P".QUESTION_ORDER				AS "RESPONSE_QUESTION_ORDER",
	"ST"."DATE",
	"ST".TARGET_LAST_MODIFIED_TS,
	"ST".MODIFIED_DATE,
	"ST".START_DATE_ID,
	"ST".END_DATE_ID,
	"ST".REVIEW_DATE_ID,
	"ST".REVIEW_STATUS,
	"ST".MANAGER_TERRITORY_ID,
	"ST".EMPLOYEE_TERRITORY_ID,
	"ST".TERRITORY_ID,
 	("ST".MODIFIED_DATE - "ST"."DATE" ) AS "DATE_DIFF",
 	CASE
 	WHEN ("ST".MODIFIED_DATE - ADD_MONTHS("ST"."DATE" - EXTRACT(DAY FROM "ST"."DATE")+1,6)) > 7 THEN 'N'
 	ELSE 'S' END AS "FLAG_PREMIO",
 	LEFT(CAST("ST".REVIEW_DATE_ID AS CHAR(8)),6)||'-'||TRIM("ST".EMPLOYEE_TERRITORY_ID) AS "SALES_FORCE_KEY",
 	LEFT(CAST("ST".REVIEW_DATE_ID AS CHAR(8)),6)||'-'||TRIM("ST".EMPLOYEE_TERRITORY_ID) AS "RESPONSES_KEY",
	'SURVEYS'				AS "ORIGEM"
    
 FROM LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_SURVEY_RESPONSES AS "P"
 
 LEFT JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT
	"P".SURVEY_TARGET_ID 					AS "SURVEY_KEY",
    "P".RESPONSE
 FROM LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_SURVEY_RESPONSES AS "P"
 WHERE "P".QUESTION_ORDER = 0  AND "P".RESPONSE IS NOT NULL) AS "PRD" ON "P".SURVEY_TARGET_ID = "PRD".SURVEY_KEY
 
 INNER JOIN (SELECT 
	  "ST".SURVEY_TARGET_ID as "SURVEY_KEY",
	  CAST(TRIM(CAST(LEFT(CAST("ST".REVIEW_DATE_ID AS CHAR(8)),4)||'-'||
	  SUBSTRING(CAST("ST".REVIEW_DATE_ID AS CHAR(8)) FROM 5 FOR 2) ||'-'||
	  RIGHT(CAST("ST".REVIEW_DATE_ID AS CHAR(8)),2) AS VARCHAR(10))) AS DATE FORMAT 'yyyy-mm-dd') AS "DATE",
	  "ST".SOURCE_LAST_MODIFIED_TS as "TARGET_LAST_MODIFIED_TS",
	  CAST("ST".SOURCE_LAST_MODIFIED_TS AS DATE FORMAT 'YYYYMMDD') AS "MODIFIED_DATE",
	  "ST".START_DATE_ID,
	  "ST".END_DATE_ID,
	  "ST".REVIEW_DATE_ID,
	  "ST".REVIEW_STATUS,
	  "ST".MANAGER_TERRITORY_ID,
	  "ST".EMPLOYEE_TERRITORY_ID,
	  "ST".TERRITORY_ID
FROM LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_SURVEY_TARGETS AS "ST"
WHERE "ST".COUNTRY_CODE = 'BR'  AND 
	"ST".SURVEY_TARGET_NAME LIKE '%GSO U%' AND
	LEFT(CAST("ST".REVIEW_DATE_ID AS CHAR(8)),6) > '201901') AS "ST" ON "P".SURVEY_TARGET_ID = "ST".SURVEY_KEY;

SELECT DISTINCT 
	TRIM(COALESCE(A.TERRITORY_ID,'')) AS "TERRITORY_ID"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(C.TERRITORY_NAME,'')) as "TERRITORY_NAME"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(B.NAME,'')) as "USER_NAME"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(B.EMAIL,'')) as "EMAIL"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(B.ALIAS_NAME,'')) as "MUDID"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(A.ACTIVE_IND,'')) as "USR_TERR_ACTIVE_IND"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(B.ACTIVE_IND,'')) as "USR_ACTIVE_IND"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(B.DELETED_IND,'')) AS "USR_DELETED_ID"
	,TRIM(COALESCE(A.USER_ID,'')) AS "USER_ID"
	,A.START_DATE as "START_DATE"
	,A.END_DATE (TITLE'') as "END_DATE"
 FROM 
	LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.SCD_USER_TERRITORY A LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_USER B
    	ON A.USER_ID = B.USER_ID
    LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_TERRITORY C
    ON	A.TERRITORY_ID = C.TERRITORY_ID;

SELECT DISTINCT
	TRIM(COALESCE(TR.FIELD_FORCE_NAME,'')) as "DIVISAO"
 	,TRIM(COALESCE(TE.TERRITORY_ID,'')) as "TERRITORY_ID"
 	,TRIM(COALESCE(TR.TERRITORY_NAME,'')) as "TERRITORIO"
 	,TRIM(COALESCE(TE.LEVEL_4_TERRITORY_NAME,'')) as "TERRITORIO_GD"
 	,TRIM(COALESCE(TE.LEVEL_5_TERRITORY_NAME,'')) as "TERRITORIO_GR"
 	,TRIM(COALESCE(TE.LEVEL_6_TERRITORY_NAME,'')) as "BU"
 	,TRIM(COALESCE(CAST(TR.END_DATE AS VARCHAR(100)),''))	(TITLE'') as "DATA_FIM_TERRITORIO"
 FROM   LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.SCD_HIERARCHY_TERRITORY TE LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_TERRITORY TR
		ON TE.TERRITORY_ID = TR.TERRITORY_ID
 WHERE 
	TE.DELETED_IND = 0 AND TE.CURRENT_IND = '1'
	AND EXISTS (SELECT A.* FROM LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_TERRITORY A WHERE TE.TERRITORY_ID = A.TERRITORY_ID AND A.ACTIVE_IND = '1');

SELECT DISTINCT
     TRIM(SAMPLE_TRANSACTION_NAME)  as "ROW_ID"
     ,''                   as "EQUIPE"
     ,''                   as "REGIONAL"
     , TRIM(A.TERRITORY_ID)      as "SETOR"
     , TRIM(A.USER_ID)            as "USER_ID"
     , ''                   as "NUM_CRM"
     , TRIM(A.SIGNATURE_DATE_ID)       as "ASSINATURA"
     , ''                   as "NOME"
     , TRIM(A.CALL_NAME)          as "ID_VISITA"
     , TRIM(A.TRANSACTION_DATE_ID)     as "DATA_DA_VISITA"
     , TRIM(A.PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID)  as "ID_MATERIAL_AMOSTRA"
     , TRIM(A.TRANSACTION_SAMPLE) as "AMOSTRA_MATERIAL_ME_MERCHANDISING"
     , TRIM(A.SAMPLE_LOT_ID)      as "LOTE"
     , TRIM(A.QUANTITY)     as "QUANTIDADE"
     , TRIM(A.ACCOUNT_ID)       as "PROF_ID" 
     , ''                   (TITLE'')       as "CATEGORIA"     
 FROM 
     LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_SAMPLE_TRANSACTION A 
 WHERE 
     A.TYPE_CD = 'Disbursement_vod' AND 
     A.DELETED_IND = '0'
 AND
     
     ((SUBSTR(CAST(A.SUBMITTED_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),1,4) = EXTRACT (YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) AND 
      SUBSTR(CAST(A.SUBMITTED_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),5,2) = EXTRACT (MONTH FROM CURRENT_DATE))
     OR
     (SUBSTR(CAST(A.SUBMITTED_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),1,4) = EXTRACT ( YEAR FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -1) ) AND 
      SUBSTR(CAST(A.SUBMITTED_DATE_ID as VARCHAR(8)),5,2) = EXTRACT ( MONTH FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -1) ) ));

SELECT DISTINCT
	TRIM(TERRITORY_ID)	as "ROW_ID_TERRITORIO" 
	,TRIM(ACCOUNT_ID)	as "ROW_ID_CONTATO"
	,TRIM(ADDRESS_ID) as "ROW_ID_ENDERECO"	
	,TRIM(MY_TARGET_IND)	(TITLE'') as "TARGET_IND"
 FROM 
	LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.H_TERR_SPECIFIC_FIELDS
 WHERE
     SOURCE_DELETED_IND = '0';

SELECT DISTINCT
     TRIM(COALESCE(A.MEDICAL_EVENT_ID,'')) as "ID_EVENTO"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.LOCATION,'')) as "LOCALIZACAO"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.EVENT_TYPE,''))  as "TIPO_EVENTO"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(OREPLACE(A.EVENT_NAME,'~','-'),'')) as "NOME_EVENTO" 
     , TRIM(COALESCE(CAST(A.START_DATE AS VARCHAR(100)),'')) as "DATA_INICIO"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(CAST(A.END_DATE AS VARCHAR(100)),'')) as "DATA_FIM"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(C.PRODUCT_NAME,'')) as "PRODUTO_PRIMARIO"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(D.PRODUCT_NAME,'')) as "PRODUTO_SECUNDARIO"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(B.TERRITORY_ID,'')) as "ROW_ID_TERRITORIO"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(B.ATTENDEE_ID,'')) as "ROW_ID_CONTATO" 
     , TRIM(COALESCE(E.RX_LEGAL_ID,'')) as "DOCUMENTO"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(B.ATTENDEE_TYPE,'')) as "TIPO_CONTA"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(B.RX_ROLE,'')) as "TIPO_PARTICIPACAO"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(B.ATTENDEE_STATUS,'')) "STATUS_CONVIDADO"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(U.NAME,'')) as "CRIADO_POR"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(U.ALIAS_NAME,'')) as "CRIADO_POR_MUDID"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(B.ATTENDEE,'')) (TITLE'') as "PARTICIPANTE"
          
 FROM 
     LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_MEDICAL_EVENT A LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_MEDICAL_EVENT_ATTENDEE B
     ON A.MEDICAL_EVENT_ID = B.MEDICAL_EVENT_ID
     
     LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_PRODUCT_CATALOG C
     ON A.RX_PRIMARY_PRODUCT = C.SOURCE_PRODUCT_CATALOG_AID
     
     LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_PRODUCT_CATALOG D
     ON A.RX_SECONDARY_PRODUCT = D.SOURCE_PRODUCT_CATALOG_AID
     
     LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_ACCOUNT E
     ON B.ATTENDEE_ID = E.ACCOUNT_ID
     
     LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_USER U
     ON A.OWNER_AID = U.SOURCE_USER_AID
     
 WHERE
     A.DELETED_IND = 0 AND B.DELETED_IND = 0
     AND
     ((EXTRACT(YEAR FROM END_DATE) = EXTRACT (YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) AND 
      EXTRACT(MONTH FROM END_DATE) = EXTRACT (MONTH FROM CURRENT_DATE))
     OR
     (EXTRACT(YEAR FROM END_DATE) = EXTRACT ( YEAR FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -1) ) AND 
      EXTRACT(MONTH FROM END_DATE) = EXTRACT ( MONTH FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -1) )));

SELECT DISTINCT 
	TRIM(COALESCE(A.ACCOUNT_ID,'')) as "ROW_ID_CONTATO"	
	, TRIM(COALESCE(CAST(A.START_DATE_ID AS VARCHAR(100)),'')) as "START_DATE"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID,'')) as "ROW_ID_PRODUTO"	
	, TRIM(COALESCE(B.PRODUCT_NAME,''))	as "PRODUCT_NAME"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(CAST(A.RX_ACTIVITY_END_TIME AS VARCHAR(100)),'')) as "END_DATE_TIME" 	
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.RX_ACTIVITY_TYPE,'')) as "ACTIVITY_TYPE"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.RX_ACTIVITY_OWNER,'')) 	as "ACTIVITY_OWNER"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.RX_TRIGGER_SOURCE_TYPE,''))  as "TRIGGER_SOURCE_TYPE"	
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.RX_DATASOURCE_CODE,'')) as "DATASOURCE_CODE"	
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.MC_ACTIVITY_NAME,''))		as "ACTIVITY_ID"
	, TRIM(COALESCE(A.URL,''))	(TITLE'') as "URL"

SELECT DISTINCT

     , TRIM(COALESCE(CAST(A.SOURCE_LAST_MODIFIED_TS AS VARCHAR(100)),''))  as "DATA_MODIFICACAO" 
     , TRIM(COALESCE(B.ACCOUNT_ID,''))   as "ROW_ID_CONTATO"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(D.ALIAS_NAME,''))   as "ROW_ID_TERRITORIO"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.QUESTION_ID,''))  as "ROW_ID_PERGUNTA" 
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.RESPONSE_NAME,''))   as "ROW_ID_RESPOSTA"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(E.QUESTION_TEXT,''))   as "PERGUNTA"
     , ''   as "PESO"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.RESPONSE_NUMBER,'')) as "RESPOSTA_NUMERICA"   
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.RESPONSE,''))   as "RESPOSTA"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.RESPONSE_TEXT,''))   as "RESPOSTA_TEXTO"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.RESPONSE_DECIMAL_VALUE,''))   as "RESPOSTA_DECIMAL"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(B.STATUS,''))  as "STATUS"
     , ''  as "RESPOSTA_FINAL"
     , TRIM(COALESCE(A.SURVEY_TARGET_ID,''))  (TITLE'') as "SURVEY_ID"
 FROM
     LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_SURVEY_RESPONSES A LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_SURVEY_TARGETS B
     ON   A.SURVEY_TARGET_ID = B.SURVEY_TARGET_ID
     
     LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_SURVEY_QUESTION E
     ON   A.QUESTION_ID = E.QUESTION_ID
     
     LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_USER D
     ON   A.SOURCE_CREATED_BY_AID = D.SOURCE_USER_AID
 WHERE
       
      ((EXTRACT(YEAR FROM A.SOURCE_CREATED_TS) = EXTRACT (YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) AND 
      EXTRACT(MONTH FROM A.SOURCE_CREATED_TS) = EXTRACT (MONTH FROM CURRENT_DATE))
     OR
     (EXTRACT(YEAR FROM A.SOURCE_CREATED_TS) = EXTRACT ( YEAR FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -1) ) AND 
      EXTRACT(MONTH FROM A.SOURCE_CREATED_TS) = EXTRACT ( MONTH FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -1) ))
     OR
     (EXTRACT(YEAR FROM A.SOURCE_CREATED_TS) = EXTRACT ( YEAR FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -1) ) AND 
      EXTRACT(MONTH FROM A.SOURCE_CREATED_TS) = EXTRACT ( MONTH FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -2) )));

      MIN(J.CUSTOMER_JOURNEY) as "CUSTOMER_JOURNEY"
      , CASE MIN(J.CUSTOMER_JOURNEY)
        WHEN 'Reach' THEN 'COMPREENS√ÉO'
        WHEN 'Acquisition' THEN 'EXPERIMENTA√á√ÉO'
        WHEN 'Conversion' THEN 'EXPANS√ÉO'
        WHEN 'Engagement' THEN 'ADES√ÉO'
  END as "JORNADA"
      , P.PRODUCT_NAME  as "PRODUTO"
      , A.RX_LEGAL_ID as "DOCUMENTO"
      , A.ID_2 as "LEGAL_ID_2"
      , A.RX_LEGACY_ID as "RX_LEGACY_ID" 
      , FIRST_NAME || ' ' || MIDDLE_NAME || ' ' || LAST_NAME as "NOME_REPRESENTANTE"
      , A.ACCOUNT_ID as "ROW_ID_CONTATO"
      , A.RX_NETWORK_AID as "NETWORKID"
      , A.RX_ACCOUNT_VEEVA_ID as "ROW_ID_CONTATO_EXT"
      , J.START_DATE as "DT_INICIO_VEEVA"
      , CURRENT_DATE as "DT_INCLUSAO"
   FROM LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.S_CUSTOMER_JOURNEY J
      LEFT JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_ACCOUNT A ON (A.ACCOUNT_ID = J.ACCOUNT_ID)
      LEFT JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_PRODUCT_CATALOG P ON (P.PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID = J.PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID)
      LEFT JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_COUNTRY C ON (C.COUNTRY_ID = J.COUNTRY_ID)
   WHERE CURRENT_DATE BETWEEN START_DATE AND END_DATE 
      AND C.COUNTRY_CODE = 'BR'
      AND CUSTOMER_JOURNEY <> 'UNSPECIFIED' 
      AND A.RX_ACCOUNT_VEEVA_ID IS NOT NULL
      AND P.COMPANY_PRODUCT_IND = '1' 
      AND P.PRODUCT_NAME IN ('BEXSERO', 'BENLYSTA', 'NUCALA', 'TIVICAY', 'NUCALA GEPA')
   GROUP BY  
      P.PRODUCT_NAME,
      A.RX_LEGAL_ID,
      A.ID_2, 
      A.RX_LEGACY_ID,
      START_DATE, 
      FIRST_NAME || ' ' || MIDDLE_NAME || ' ' || LAST_NAME,
      A.ACCOUNT_ID, 
      A.RX_NETWORK_AID, 
      A.RX_ACCOUNT_VEEVA_ID 
   ORDER BY START_DATE DESC;

select *  
    FROM LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_EM_EVENT;

SELECT DISTINCT 
                TRIM(COALESCE(A.MEDICAL_EVENT_ID,''))                  AS "ID_EVENTO",
                TRIM(COALESCE(A.LOCATION,''))                          AS "LOCALIZACAO",
                TRIM(COALESCE(A.EVENT_TYPE,''))                        AS "TIPO_EVENTO",
                TRIM(COALESCE(OREPLACE(A.EVENT_NAME,'~','-'),''))      AS "NOME_EVENTO",
                TRIM(COALESCE(CAST(A.START_DATE AS VARCHAR(100)),''))  AS "DATA_INICIO",
                TRIM(COALESCE(CAST(A.END_DATE AS VARCHAR(100)),''))    AS "DATA_FIM",
                TRIM(COALESCE(C.PRODUCT_NAME,''))                      AS "PRODUTO_PRIMARIO",
                TRIM(COALESCE(D.PRODUCT_NAME,''))                      AS "PRODUTO_SECUNDARIO",
                TRIM(COALESCE(B.TERRITORY_ID,''))                      AS "ROW_ID_TERRITORIO",
                TRIM(COALESCE(B.ATTENDEE_ID,''))                       AS "ROW_ID_CONTATO",
                TRIM(COALESCE(E.RX_LEGAL_ID,''))                       AS "DOCUMENTO",
                TRIM(COALESCE(B.ATTENDEE_TYPE,''))                     AS "TIPO_CONTA",
                TRIM(COALESCE(B.RX_ROLE,''))                           AS "TIPO_PARTICIPACAO",
                TRIM(COALESCE(B.ATTENDEE_STATUS,''))                   AS "STATUS_CONVIDADO",
                TRIM(COALESCE(U.NAME,''))                              AS "CRIADO_POR",
                TRIM(COALESCE(U.ALIAS_NAME,''))                        AS "CRIADO_POR_MUDID",
                TRIM(COALESCE(B.ATTENDEE,''))                          AS "PARTICIPANTE",
                TRIM(COALESCE(B.RX_ATTENDEE_SPECIALTY,''))             AS "ESPECIALIDADE" 
                               
    FROM  
                LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_MEDICAL_EVENT A LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_MEDICAL_EVENT_ATTENDEE B
                ON A.MEDICAL_EVENT_ID = B.MEDICAL_EVENT_ID
                
                LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_PRODUCT_CATALOG C
                ON A.RX_PRIMARY_PRODUCT = C.SOURCE_PRODUCT_CATALOG_AID
                
                LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_PRODUCT_CATALOG D
                ON A.RX_SECONDARY_PRODUCT = D.SOURCE_PRODUCT_CATALOG_AID
                
                LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_ACCOUNT E
                ON B.ATTENDEE_ID = E.ACCOUNT_ID
                
                LEFT OUTER JOIN LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_USER U
                ON A.OWNER_AID = U.SOURCE_USER_AID
                
    WHERE  
       A.DELETED_IND = 0 AND B.DELETED_IND = 0
       AND
          EXTRACT(YEAR FROM END_DATE) >= EXTRACT ( YEAR FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -8)) 
       AND
          EXTRACT(MONTH FROM END_DATE) >= EXTRACT ( MONTH FROM ADD_MONTHS (CURRENT_DATE , -8));
